  "transcript": {
    "language": "en",
    "is_generated": false,
    "segments": [
      {
        "start": 0.3,
        "duration": 1.5,
        "text": "- Hi, I'm Fernando,\n(gentle uplifting music)"
      },
      {
        "start": 1.8,
        "duration": 2.5,
        "text": "a district success\nmanager with Khan Academy."
      },
      {
        "start": 4.3,
        "duration": 2.9,
        "text": "Welcome to Khan Academy Reimagined."
      },
      {
        "start": 7.2,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "Now, before we get into what's improving,"
      },
      {
        "start": 9.9,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "let me just say I get it."
      },
      {
        "start": 12.3,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "I spent the last 14 years as a teacher"
      },
      {
        "start": 14.7,
        "duration": 1.5,
        "text": "and as an administrator."
      },
      {
        "start": 16.2,
        "duration": 1.1,
        "text": "I love Khan Academy"
      },
      {
        "start": 17.3,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "for its trusted standards-aligned content,"
      },
      {
        "start": 20.0,
        "duration": 1.3,
        "text": "and I know you do too,"
      },
      {
        "start": 21.3,
        "duration": 1.2,
        "text": "but let's face it,"
      },
      {
        "start": 22.5,
        "duration": 2.9,
        "text": "students didn't always\nfind it engaging and fun."
      },
      {
        "start": 25.4,
        "duration": 3.2,
        "text": "For teachers, it felt\ncrowded and hard to navigate."
      },
      {
        "start": 28.6,
        "duration": 3.6,
        "text": "We're keeping the core of what\nyou love, the great content,"
      },
      {
        "start": 32.2,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "along with the support of the latest AI,"
      },
      {
        "start": 34.6,
        "duration": 1.7,
        "text": "and we've redesigned everything else"
      },
      {
        "start": 36.3,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "based off of years of your feedback."
      },
      {
        "start": 38.5,
        "duration": 0.9,
        "text": "We heard you."
      },
      {
        "start": 39.4,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "The clutter and noise is gone."
      },
      {
        "start": 41.3,
        "duration": 2.6,
        "text": "Your new teacher dashboard\nis simple, intuitive,"
      },
      {
        "start": 44.0,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "and designed to give you back time."
      },
      {
        "start": 45.9,
        "duration": 1.7,
        "text": "You'll see the Khanmigo search window,"
      },
      {
        "start": 47.6,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "your one-stop shop for\npowerful lesson planning,"
      },
      {
        "start": 50.0,
        "duration": 1.8,
        "text": "content discovery, and more."
      },
      {
        "start": 51.9,
        "duration": 2.1,
        "text": "Right below that, your\ninsights for the day."
      },
      {
        "start": 54.0,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "This takes all of the guesswork"
      },
      {
        "start": 55.6,
        "duration": 2.1,
        "text": "out of where your students need support."
      },
      {
        "start": 57.8,
        "duration": 2.5,
        "text": "Forget endless data analysis."
      },
      {
        "start": 60.2,
        "duration": 1.8,
        "text": "You'll still get the same reporting,"
      },
      {
        "start": 62.0,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "but our AI processes the data for you,"
      },
      {
        "start": 64.3,
        "duration": 2.6,
        "text": "telling you exactly\nwhich students need help"
      },
      {
        "start": 66.9,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "and providing the precise exercises"
      },
      {
        "start": 68.7,
        "duration": 1.5,
        "text": "to get them back on track."
      },
      {
        "start": 70.2,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "With one push of a button,"
      },
      {
        "start": 71.8,
        "duration": 3.5,
        "text": "you can even directly assign\nan AI-powered tutoring session."
      },
      {
        "start": 75.3,
        "duration": 3.4,
        "text": "It's like having a data analyst\nand a tutor in your corner."
      },
      {
        "start": 78.6,
        "duration": 2.6,
        "text": "You still keep a close eye on\nwhat your students are saying"
      },
      {
        "start": 81.3,
        "duration": 1.5,
        "text": "back and forth with Khanmigo,"
      },
